    "department": "Other",
    "description": "ABOUT US\n\nParallel is a web infrastructure company. Our products are used by leading businesses in sales, marketing, insurance, and coding to build best-in-class AI agents with flexible and powerful programmatic access to the web.\n\nWe've raised $130 million from Kleiner Perkins, Index Ventures, Spark Capital, Khosla Ventures, First Round, and Terrain to build the web for AIs. We're forming a world-class team of engineers, designers, marketers, sellers, researchers, and operational experts to achieve our mission.\n\nJob: Our first internal recruiter hire. You will shape our hiring process and systems, build a world-class talent brand, and hire an amazing team. You will understand our culture and product needs deeply to find the right talent for our stage. You will be the primary architect of how we scale.\n\nYou: Love the \"blank canvas\" stage of a startup. You are a recruiter by training but also may have worked in branding, operations, or roles that require building systems from scratch. You care most about owning the candidate experience and long-term team impact.\n\n\nLIFE AT PARALLEL\n\nOur team works fully in-person, between our Palo Alto HQ and San Francisco office. We’re a flat, talent-dense organization dedicated to solving technical and creative problems.\n\nWe seek like-minded individuals who share our passion for applying science, creativity, and consistency to big and complex problems with equally big outcomes. These are our values:\n\n - Own customer impact: It’s on us to ensure real-world outcomes for our customers.\n\n - Obsess over craft: Perfect every detail because quality compounds.\n\n - Accelerate change: Ship fast, adapt faster, and move frontier ideas into production.\n\n - Create win-wins: Creatively turn trade-offs into upside.\n\n - Make high-conviction bets: Try and fail. But succeed an unfair amount.\n\n\nCOMPENSATION \u0026 BENEFITS\n\n - Competitive salary\n\n - Generous equity\n\n - Visa sponsorships\n\n - 401K plans\n\n - Daily lunch \u0026 office snacks\n\n - Dinner at the office\n\n - Unlimited vacation\n\n - Caltrain pass reimbursement",
    "employment_type": "FullTime",
